WEBVTT

00:00:01.807 --> 00:00:06.339
We are all here today
because the climate countdown has begun,

00:00:06.363 --> 00:00:09.158
and we are nowhere near
where we need to be.

00:00:09.710 --> 00:00:12.320
Science tells us
we must limit to global heating

00:00:12.344 --> 00:00:15.916
to 1.5 degrees Celsius
above pre-industrial levels.

00:00:16.352 --> 00:00:19.543
We are on track
for three degrees at least.

00:00:19.567 --> 00:00:21.270
Billions of people around the world

00:00:21.294 --> 00:00:23.850
are already suffering
from our failure to act.

00:00:24.449 --> 00:00:28.946
Climate disruption, due to our outdated
addiction to fossil fuels,

00:00:28.970 --> 00:00:31.646
is causing unprecedented wildfires,